<div id="usf-sport-marketing-details" class="project-details-section">
  <h2>USF Sport Marketing Details</h2>

  <div class="card-section">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Association Description</h3>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..1).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/slide 34/#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Image" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Welcome screen and quick information about the mission of the association.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-section">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Events / Giveaways</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..2).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/slide 35/#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Image" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Executives can easily share networking events, guest speakers, and any other events with members of the association. A section for giveaways is accessible if the executive team decides to find interactive ways to engage with the community.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Articles</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..3).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/slide 36/#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Image" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Articles from sport management students and members of the association can be posted in this section to provide insightful information in the industry.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="section-title">Exercises</h3>

  <div class="card-section">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Team Roster</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..3).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/slide 37/#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Image" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Bio and personalized information on each of the executives of the USF Sport Marketing Association team.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Join / Reach Out</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..3).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/slide 38/#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Image" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>This screen provides an easy way to access additional resources provided to members. There is also a direct link to inquire about relevant information through a direct in-app prefilled email communication channel.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-section">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Admin Account</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..3).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/slide 39/#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Image" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Executives of the team are provided with a universal login to change the data of the app. The login makes it easy to pass details to future generations of executives and makes the app future-proof.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Fully Modular UI</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..3).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/slide 40/#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Image" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Executives can easily add and remove data from the app given their needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Quick Forms to Update Data</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..5).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/slide 41/#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Image" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Forms were created so the executives can pass on all the required information for executive bio, articles, events, and giveaways. The form for each section was specifically customized to fit properly with a flawless UX.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Released on the Apple Store</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..2).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/slide 42/#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Image" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>The app is currently posted on the Apple Store and has received very positive feedback from users and members of the association.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="section-title">Website</h3>

  <div class="card-section">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Association Website</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..4).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/sma/sma#{i}.png") %>" alt="USF Sport Marketing Website" class="sma-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>The USF Sport Marketing Association website serves as the digital hub for the organization, featuring comprehensive information about the team, upcoming events, member benefits, and ways to get involved. The website showcases the association's mission to explore the sport marketing industry while providing a platform for networking and professional development opportunities.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="navigation-buttons">
    <a href="#ripped-utopia-details" class="nav-button left-button">← Check Ripped Utopia Project</a>
    <a href="#easyfind-details" class="nav-button right-button">Check EasyFind Project →</a>
  </div>
</div>
